quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  26,176,Ashaab-ul-Aiyqah ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,177,Yaad karo jabke Shoaib ne unse kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin
  26,178,Main tumhare liye ek amanat-daar Rasool hoon
  26,179,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,180,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,181,Paimane theek bharo (Give full measure) aur kisi ko ghaata (less) na do
  26,182,Saheeh tarazu se tolo
  26,183,"Aur logon ko unki cheezein kam na do, zameen mein fasaad na phaylate phiro"
  26,184,Aur us zaat ka khauff karo jisne tumhein aur guzishta nasalon ko paida kiya hai.”
  26,185,Unhon ne kaha “tu mehaz ek sehar zadah(affected by magic) aadmi hai
  26,186,"Aur tu kuch nahin magar ek Insaan hum hi jaisa, aur hum to tujhey bilkul jhoota samajhte hain"
  26,187,Agar tu saccha hai to humpar aasmaan ka koi tukda gira de”
  26,188,Shoaib ne kaha “ mera Rubb jaanta hai jo kuch tum kar rahey ho”
  26,189,"Unhon ne usey jhutla diya, aakhir-e-kaar chatri waley din (Day of Canopy) ka azaab unpar aa gaya, aur woh baday hi khauf-naak din ka azaab tha"
  26,190,"Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar log maanne waley nahin"
  26,191,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi